author: @kleinebre
text: This is not only interesting from an investing strategy perspective, but it also teaches you a thing or two about coding. It starts with a forgotten `else` case... then the code duplication creeps in. Then, the globals. In this video, we have our first stack trace.  Don't try this at home, kids. Keep your code clean.
